#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:495
msgid "**LLM quantization**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:497
msgid ""
"Download the original floating-point weights of the large model. Taking "
"Qwen3-32B as an example, you can go to [Qwen3-32B](https://huggingface.co/"
"Qwen/Qwen3-32B) to obtain the original model weights. Then install other "
"dependencies (related to the model, refer to the huggingface model card)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:498
msgid ""
"Note: You can find pre-quantized validated models on [modelscope/Eco-Tech]"
"(https://modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:500
msgid ""
"_Traditional quantification methods require the preparation of calibration "
"data files (```.jsonl``` formats) for calibration in the quantification "
"process._"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:501
msgid ""
"Qwen3-32B/      # floating-point model downloaded from official HF (or "
"modelscope) repo\n"
"msmodelslim/    # msmodelslim repo\n"
"  |----- lab_calib # calibration date folder (put your dataset here in ```."
"jsonl``` format or use pre-prepared ones)\n"
"      |----- some file (such as laos_calib.jsonl)\n"
"  |----- lab_practice # best practice folder with configs for quantization\n"
"      |----- model folder (such as qwen3_5_moe folder) # folder with "
"quantization configs\n"
"          |----- quant_config (such as qwen3_5_moe_w8a8.yaml) # quantization "
"config\n"
"  |----- another folders\n"
"output_folder/   # generated by below command\n"
"  |----- quant_model_weights-00001-of-0001.safetensors # quantized weights\n"
"  |----- quant_model_description.json # file with description of the "
"quantization methods for each layer (```W4A4_DYNAMIC```, etc.)\n"
"  |----- another files (such as config.json, tokenizer.json, etc.)\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:515
msgid "Run quantization using one-click quantization (recommended):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:516
msgid ""
"msmodelslim quant \\\n"
"--model_path ${MODEL_PATH} \\\n"
"--save_path ${SAVE_PATH} \\\n"
"--device npu:0,1 \\\n"
"--model_type Qwen3-32B \\\n"
"--quant_type w8a8 \\\n"
"--trust_remote_code True\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:526
msgid "**Usage Example**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced_features/quantization.md:527
msgid ""
"python3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\n"
"--model-path $PWD/Qwen3-32B-w8a8 \\\n"
"--port 30000 --host 0.0.0.0\n"
msgstr ""

